    "title": [
      "[Hinterwilds, Boreal Forest]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "The cries of owls and the rustle of rodents fill the air of the gelid woodland.  Nests rock in the boughs of several of the surrounding firs, cobbled together from twigs and bits of twine.  Marching beneath the wild dance of the aurora as it ripples across an unforgiving black sky, the little-trodden path verges on a crystalline briar to the southwest."
